'''热带风暴泰米'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Tammy}}）是2005年10月上旬一个持续时间较为短暂[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年大西洋飓风季]]第19场获得命名的风暴。气旋只对[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]构成轻微影响，但其残留之后同[[冷锋|冷锋]]合并而产生大量降水，促使[[美国东北部|美国东北部]]爆发[[2005年10月美国东北部洪灾|严重洪灾]]。

气旋于10月5日在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]近海由不具备热带特征的天气系统发展而成，起初在距海岸线不远处向北移动一段时间，再于当天晚上[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。风暴在陆地上空迅速减弱，到次日便已消散。泰米的残余[[大气环流|环流]]朝[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]方向南下，其水分在此期间被向东北方向移动的冷锋吸收。泰米没有直接导致人员丧生，但风暴残留同第二十二号热带低气压共同影响，间接致使10人遇难。整场风暴共计造成的经济损失约为3000万美元。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Tammy 2005 track.png}}
2005年9月24日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸，在经过[[大西洋|大西洋]]期间没有得到任何发展。10月2日，东北波在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以北接触上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]并开始发展。10月5日清晨经过[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]时，系统已有强化，发展出苍劲蓬勃的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]。<ref name="TammyTCR">{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Tammy | accessdate = 2015-12-14 | date = 2006-01-28 | format = PDF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL222005_Tammy.pdf | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011813/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL222005_Tammy.pdf | deadurl = no}}</ref>系统内的风速已经达到热带风暴强度，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此立即将之归类为热带风暴并以“泰米”（{{lang|en|Tammy}}）命名。虽已成为热带风暴，但气旋组织结构仍然相当混乱，只有环流中心东南方向有深层[[对流|对流]]持续。附近船只测得的风速最高也只有每小时55公里，气象机构因此预计泰米内部的热带风暴强度风力局限在对流下方。风暴快速向西北方向移动，路线两侧的一边是[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空的中到上层[[低气压|低气压]]，另一边则是西大西洋上空的[[高压脊|高压脊]]，还受到两个天气系统之间的南向气流影响。<ref>{{cite report | author = Knabb | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-14 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Special Discussion One | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111115/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref>当天下午，飞入风暴的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得飞行高度层风速为每小时98公里，相当于每小时85公里的地面风速。此外，侦察机还测得时速95至100公里的小范围风场。<ref>{{cite report | author = Franklin | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Discussion Three | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111120/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref>[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]当晚23点，泰米以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里强度从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[大西洋海滩_(佛罗里达州)|大西洋海滩]]附近登陆<ref name="TammyTCR" />。气旋接下来进入[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]上空<ref>{{cite report | author = Knabb | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-06 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Advisory Number 5 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.005.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111131/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.005.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>，再从[[欧扎克山区|欧扎克山区]]附近进入[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]东南部<ref>{{cite report | author = Franklin | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111133/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.006.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-06 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Advisory Number 6 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.006.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref>，其环流于10月6日在该州境内消散<ref name="TammyTCR" />。

残留低气压向南面的[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]飘移，并逐渐被已吸收[[2005年大西洋飓风季的风暴#第二十二号亚热带低气压|第二十二号亚热带低气压]]的一股[[冷锋|冷锋]]吸收。冷锋向东北方向移动，在之后几天里对[[美国东北部|美国东北部]]大范围地区构成影响。<ref name="TammyTCR" /><ref name="NHC-disc6">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | title = Discussion for Tropical Storm Tammy, 11 a.m. EDT, October 6, 2005 | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111135/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al212005.discus.006.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref>

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Tammy-radar.gif|thumb]]
10月5日热带风暴泰米的形成出乎许多气象学家预料<ref name="TammyTCR" />，他们起初都认为其热带扰动前身不会发展，以至风暴实际[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前12小时才开始发布警报<ref name="public01" /><ref name="public03a">{{cite report | author = Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111113/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public_a.003.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Intermediate Advisory Number 3A | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public_a.003.shtml?}}</ref>。不过警报时间虽短，许多游客和商务旅客还是在风暴即将登陆时退订航班<ref>{{cite news|author=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022051346/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C171276%2C00.html |publisher=Fox News |date=2005-10-05 |accessdate=2015-12-15 |title=Tropical Storm Tammy Slams Into Florida |deadurl=no |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/10/05/tropical-storm-tammy-slams-into-florida.html |archivedate=2012-10-22 }}</ref>。风暴发展同时，佛罗里达州[[可可比奇|可可比奇]]到[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[桑蒂河|桑蒂河]]（{{lang|en|Santee River}}）之间沿海地区很快接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="public01">{{cite report | author = Knabb | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2005-10-05 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Special Advisory Number 1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002111110/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al212005.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

[[美国国土安全部|美国国土安全部]]下属的第7区[[美国海岸警卫队|海岸警卫队]]向海员发布公告，警告他们做好应对风暴的准备，并且非必要情况下不要出海<ref>{{cite web | author = Petty Officer Bobby Nash | publisher = Office of Public Affairs, U.S. Coast Guard Seventh District | date = 2005-10-05 | accessdate = 2008-08-20 | title = Coast Guard Urges Mariners to Prepare for Tammy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120729111119/http://www.piersystem.com/go/doc/586/84931/ | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.piersystem.com/go/doc/586/84931/ | archivedate = 2012-07-29}}</ref>。[[美国国家公园管理局|国家公园管理局]]将[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[坎伯兰岛|坎伯兰岛]]（{{lang|en|Cumberland Island}}）的居民疏散，并暂时关闭岛上的轮渡服务。[[格林县_(乔治亚州)|格林县]]应急行动署密切监控泰米的动向，为气旋登陆做准备，但由于警告发布不及时，当地防灾准备工作受到不良影响。该州各地居民都对没有充分时间做准备感到不满。<ref name="news4jax_little_time">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = News 4 Georgia | date = 2005-10-05 | accessdate = 2011-09-27 | title = Ga. Residents, Officials Brace For Tammy | url = http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/5062769/detail.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927152239/http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/5062769/detail.html | archivedate = 2011-09-27}}</ref>泰米于12小时后登岸时<ref name="public03a" />，热带风暴警告生效范围向北扩展至乔治亚州阿特马哈湾（{{lang|en|Altamaha Sound}}），10月6日，之前发布的所有警告均已取消<ref name="TammyTCR" />。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Tammy_2005_rainfall.gif|right]]

热带风暴泰米造成的破坏程度很轻，产生的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]为每小时80公里，测得的最强阵风时速则为97公里<ref name="TammyTCR" />。大风没有造成显著破坏，但有1万6500 户电力客户的供电受到干扰<ref name="palm_beach_summary">{{cite web | author = Staff Writers | publisher = Palm Beach Post | title = Tammy recap | date = 2008-10-22 | url = http://www.palmbeachpost.com/storm/content/storm/2005/atlantic/tammy/news.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120306022847/http://www.palmbeachpost.com/storm/content/storm/2005/atlantic/tammy/news.html | archivedate = 2012-03-06 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-03-06}}</ref>，泰塞尔学院的帆船比赛也被迫延迟<ref>{{cite web | author = Marcy Trenholm | publisher = Larchmont Gazette | date = 2008-10-11 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | url = http://www.larchmontgazette.com/2005/articles/20051012trysail.html | archivedate = 2012-02-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120211094710/http://www.larchmontgazette.com/2005/articles/20051012trysail.html | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Challenges Trysail College Regatta}}</ref>。风暴产生的[[闪电|闪电]]击中[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]][[椰子溪_(佛罗里达州)|椰子溪]]一场足球赛上的3名少年，导致1死2伤<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = NCDC Event Report: Florida Lightning}}</ref>。

佛罗里达州北部和乔治亚州南部大部分地区的降雨量为76到127毫米，部分地区达到250毫米<ref name="rainfall_diego">{{cite web | author = Russ Bynum | publisher = San Diego Union-Tribune | date = 2005-10-06 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy brings heavy rain, gusts to Georgia | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121016224914/http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/nation/20051006-0813-tropicalweather.html | url = http://legacy.utsandiego.com/news/nation/20051006-0813-tropicalweather.html | archivedate = 2012-10-16 }}</ref>。乔治亚州格林县[[县城|县城]][[不伦瑞克_(乔治亚州)|不伦瑞克]]（{{lang|en|Brunswick}}）有30余幢房屋因洪灾受损<ref name="flooded_homes">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | publisher = St. Petersburg Times | date = 2005-10-07 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tammy causes flooding in south Georgia | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104001423/http://www.sptimes.com/2005/10/07/Weather/Tammy_causes_flooding.shtml | url = http://www.sptimes.com/2005/10/07/Weather/Tammy_causes_flooding.shtml}}</ref>。多条泥土砌成的道路和沿海公路被洪水冲毁<ref name="rainfall_diego" />，向北远至[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]的[[巴尔的摩县_(马里兰州)|巴尔的摩县]]都有下水道溢出<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Hindustan Times | date = 2008-10-09 | title = Sewers Overwhelmed by Tropical Storm Tammy}}</ref>。两口小型池塘的水坝坍塌，其中1个木质水坝已有173年历史，不过老坝决堤前，当地已经修建新的石质水坝<ref name="palm_beach_summary" />。泰米产生的降水总体对南卡罗莱纳州有利，缓解了当地的旱情<ref>{{cite news | author = Rowland Alston | publisher = The State | date = 2005-10-16 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Dry Gardens Finally get a Soaking | page = G3 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CS&s_site=thestate&p_multi=CS&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=10D4D51B66D1A710&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210402102253/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CS&s_site=thestate&p_multi=CS&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=10D4D51B66D1A710&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>，当地整个9月都没有降雨<ref>{{cite web | author = Computer Generated | publisher = Weather Underground | title = History for KSCCLEMS1 | date = 2005-10-01 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | url = http://www.wunderground.com/personal-weather-station/dashboard?ID=KSCCLEMS1 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150819081136/http://www.wunderground.com/personal-weather-station/dashboard?ID=KSCCLEMS1 | archivedate = 2015-08-19}}</ref>。

泰米产生的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]约有0.61至1.22米高，造成海水在佛罗里达州东北部、乔治亚州和南卡罗莱纳州沿海地区泛滥<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = NCDC Event Report: Georgia Tropical Storm}}</ref>。风暴潮令沿海木板桥受损，海浪还导致0.6米深的海滩受到[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]<ref name="TammyTCR" />。除引发洪灾外，气旋还催生出1场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Tom Grazulis | author2 = Bill McCaul | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151129203217/http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | publisher = The Tornado Project | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = List of Known Tropical Cyclones Which Have Spawned Tornadoes | url = http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | archivedate = 2015-11-29 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。这场[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|F0}}的龙卷风在不伦瑞克附近着陆，刮断多棵树木的同时，还令3.2公里移动路线上的多座房屋屋顶受到中等程度破坏<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = NCDC Event Report: Georgia Tornado}}</ref>。估计整场风暴一共造成价值3000万美元左右的损失<ref name="TammyTCR" />，气旋外围[[雨带|雨带]]还产生暴雨，部分地区最高降雨量达180毫米<ref name="HPC">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorlogical Prediction Center | year = 2005 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Tropical Storm Tammy Rainfall | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//tammy2005.html | archivedate = 2015-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210121724/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tammy2005.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>，造成严重的海滩侵蚀。沿海地区的阵风时速最高有95公里，刮倒了许多树木。情况最严重的是[[博福特县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|博福特县]]，有30棵树倒塌，其中1棵还倒在民房上。恶劣的海况还令多幢位于海滩上的房屋受损，其中1幢被淹<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2006 | title = NCDC Event Report: South Carolina Tropical Storm}}</ref>。

== 善后、命名和纪录 ==
风暴过去后，乔治亚州不伦瑞克的红十字会避难所开放两天，为房屋被淹的居民提供临时住宿<ref name="red_x">{{cite web | author = Associated Press | publisher = News4Jax | date = 2005-10-07 | accessdate = 2011-09-27 | title = Flooding Continues Two Days After Tropical Storm Moves On | url = http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/5073567/detail.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927152411/http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/5073567/detail.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-09-27}}</ref>。气旋的残留低气压被向北移动的更大规模[[温带气旋|温带低气压]]吸收，在[[美国东北部|美国东北部]]产生大量降水并引发严重洪灾，导致10人遇难和严重破坏<ref name="TammyTCR" />。受这些洪灾影响，[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]提供了4400万美元修复资金<ref>{{cite web | author = FEMA | publisher = FEMA | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120716194401/http://www.fema.gov/business/nfip/statistics/sign1000.shtm | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.fema.gov/business/nfip/statistics/sign1000.shtm | date = 2008-08-11 | accessdate = 2012-07-16 | title = FEMA: Significant Flood Events | archivedate = 2012-07-16}}</ref>。

2005年，南、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的捕虾从业人士面临包括油价上涨在内的多种困境，他们认为热带风暴泰米便是这一困境的罪魁祸首之一。不断上涨的燃油价格和需求萎缩本已令捕虾业举步维艰，泰米的到来又令捕捞工作被迫中断数日，对局势雪上加霜。<ref>{{cite news | author = Kelly Marshall | newspaper = The Sun News | date = 2008-10-09 | title = Experts: Local shrimpers face another tough year}}</ref>

热带风暴泰米于10月5日成形，创下单个大西洋飓风季中形成日期最早的第20场风暴纪录<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Vance Publishing | date = 2005-10-12 | title = National Weather: Heavy Snow Dropped On Northern Plains}}</ref><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122222210/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-060415.txt | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2015-12-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-060415.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-06-04 | archivedate = 2015-11-22 | format = TXT}}</ref>，比[[1933年大西洋飓风季|1933年大西洋飓风季]]创下的原纪录要早21天<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Edward N. Rappaport | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131126075456/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1933.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1933 | archivedate = 2013-11-26 | format = PDF | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1933.pdf}}</ref><ref name="HURDAT" />。

